\par }\pard \sl360\slmult1 {\b\f5\fs20 New
\par }\pard {\f5\fs20 Randomly chooses 8 new cubes and starts a new game.
\par 
\par }\pard \sl360\slmult1 {\b\f5\fs20 Reset}{\f5\fs20 
\par }\pard {\f5\fs20 Merely removes all small cubes from the large cube (if any) and places them back at the top of the screen.  This option allows an easy way to start over on the same game.
\par }\pard {\f5\fs20 
\par }\pard \sl360\slmult1 {\b\f5\fs20 Solve}{\f5\fs20 
\par }\pard {\f5\fs20 Provides an animated solution to the current game.  During the animation, the Exit and Help menu options are still available.
\par }\pard {\f5\fs20 
